股市場參與者在「惡劣天氣不停市」的安排下，盡早作出運營及人力資源調配，支持市場平穩運作。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;港交所會密切監察最新情況，與證監會及市場參與者保持緊密聯繫。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;香港證券及期貨專業總會發聲明指，關注港股維持打風不停市的安排，認為需要保障從業人員及公眾的安全。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;本港去年九月實行「惡劣天氣不停市」安排，以讓本港證券市場進一步與國際接軌。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32040098&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=101286019768d17a106aee03_18865228"/><published>2025-09-22T22:55:14+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>cc774b72c417cf4a5ad30bc6c0189d01</id><title>有證券業人士認為港股短線部署不宜過於進取</title><updated>2025-09-22T22:59:11+08:00</updated><author><name>胡三刀</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-09-22T22:59:11+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_574077804"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_574077804"&gt;有證券業人士認為港股短線部署不宜過於進取&lt;br&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://news.tvb.com/tc/finance/68d0cd3e47520861d41b733c?utm_source=newsappshare&amp;amp;utm_medium=referral" target="_blank" uhash="1f9f099f120ecd23bc4557f630b9605d"&gt;https://news.tvb.com/tc/finance/68d0cd3e47520861d41b733c?utm_source=newsappshare&amp;amp;utm_medium=referral&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32040100&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=101286019768d17a106aee03_18865228"/><published>2025-09-22T22:59:11+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>0acb7d6fc44e34daa4631b297ccacb28</id><title>陳國基籲僱主情理兼備：員工為佢賺錢 佢都過意唔去</title><updated>2025-09-22T23:09:09+08:00</updated><author><name>realty86</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-09-22T23:09:09+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-conte